8:21.192Z\",\"url\":\"http://localhost:3000/dashboard\",\"dsl\":\"@ Next\\n! Next\",\"tape\":[{\"t\":0,\"fn\":\"scene\",\"args\":[[{\"match\":\"Next\"},{\"click\":{\"match\":\"Next\"}}]]}]},{\"ts\":\"2026-05-25T01:08:37.048Z\",\"url\":\"http://localhost:3000/dashboard\",\"dsl\":\"\\n  > Step 5 — Settlement. $25,412 saved over 3 years. No job offer. No PNP. No sibling. Just savings and determination.\\n  @ Settlement details\\n  \\\"3 $25,412 CAD. Three years of savings. Every naira I didn't spend on myself.\\n  = Settlement Funds Available | 25412\\n  @ Valid job offer\\n  \\\"3 No job offer. No employer backing me. Zero additional points.\\n  @ Provincial/territorial nomination\\n  \\\"3 No provincial nomination. No 600-point boost. Just the raw score.\\n  @ Sibling\\n  \\\"3 No sibling in Canada. Just Tunde — a friend, not family for CRS purposes.\\n\",\"tape\":[{\"t\":0,\"fn\":\"scene\",\"args\":[[{\"narrate\":\"Step 5 — Settlement. $25,412 saved over 3 years. No job offer. No PNP. No sibling. Just savings and determination.\"},{\"match\":\"Settlement details\",\"thought\":\"$25,412 CAD. Three years of savings. Every naira I didn't spend on myself.\",\"duration\":3000},{\"fill\":{\"match\":\"Settlement Funds Available\"},\"value\":\"25412\"},{\"match\":\"Valid job offer\",\"thought\":\"No job offer. No employer backing me. Zero additional points.\",\"duration\":3000},{\"match\":\"Provincial/territorial nomination\",\"thought\":\"No provincial nomination. No 600-point boost. Just the raw score.\",\"duration\":3000},{\"match\":\"Sibling\",\"thought\":\"No sibling in Canada. Just Tunde — a friend, not family for CRS purposes.\",\"duration\":3000}]]}]},{\"ts\":\"2026-05-25T01:09:00.261Z\",\"url\":\"http://localhost:3000/dashboard\",\"dsl\":\"\\n  \\\"3 Ontario. Toronto. Where Tunde is. Where the Nigerian tech community is.\\n  \\\"5 Five steps done. No job offer, no PNP, no sibling, no French. Just me, my IELTS, my Master's, and my six years at Interswitch. Let's see